I'm a software engineer based in London, UK specializing in building (and occasionally designing) exceptional websites, applications, and everything in between. I have an unending passion for building web applications and improving user experiences.

About Me

I enjoy creating things that live on the internet, whether that be websites, applications, or anything in between. My goal is to always build products that provide pixel-perfect, performant experiences.

Shortly after graduating from De Montfort University, I dedicated a whole year to just perfecting my craft in Javascript (React) by building projects and improving my communication(stuttering) by creating content, i.e., teaching coding on Youtube.

Outside of web development and my career - I enjoy reading and writing, practicing teaching, football, and table-tennis. Please find out more about me by viewing some of my recent projects below.
